\int_E |f_n - f| \to 0
\lim_{n\to\infty} \int_E |f_n| = \int_E |f|
0\le\left|\int_{E}|f_n|-\int_{E}|f|\right|= \left|\int_{E}(|f_n|-|f|)\right| \le \int_{E}|f_n-f|.
\int_{E}|f_n-f|\to 0 \quad \Rightarrow \int_{E}|f_n|\to \int_{E}|f|.
\int_{E}|f_n|\to \int_{E}|f|.
